{"tid":647783,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"翹臀IG女模被控人獸交！拍攝中玩弄狗狗生殖器　飼主求償4千萬","createTime":"2018-04-30T06:40:15.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-30T08:05:25.000Z","uid":1121,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"dd537d6d10623fb5ce9f8b56575110cf36c27462","tid":647783,"uid":1121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T06:40:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3256/d3256852.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3256%2Fd3256852.jpg&h=b7dd38c5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲黎巴嫩IG辣模戴雅娜被指控人獸交。（圖／翻攝自Deyana Mounira IG）<br />\n<br />\n國際中心／綜合報導<br />\n<br />\n美國一名商人東尼（Tony Toutouni）日前邀請一名黎巴嫩IG辣模戴雅娜（Deyana Mounira），前來自己的豪宅游泳池拍攝性感照片，結果戴雅娜卻與他養的寵物狗發生人獸交，氣得他決定向法院提起訴訟、要求150萬美元（約4433萬元新台幣）精神賠償。對此，戴雅娜則表示是東尼說謊。<br />\n<br />\n綜合外媒報導，戴雅娜經常在Instagram上分享自己的火辣身材，展現自己擁有的巨乳豐臀好身材，因此吸引許多網友追蹤、網路上小有名氣，但是日前她接受東尼邀請，前往東尼的豪宅拍攝性感照片後，東尼卻指控她與現場一隻「黑俄羅斯梗」發生人獸交，要求精神賠償150萬美元。"},{"pid":"be8ac2ddd6bc11c5a697589d33333bd15936d471","tid":647783,"uid":131323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T06:41:53.000Z","msg":"精神賠償係隻狗定個人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29ca2cf75eb55b6c8b92791373ec94bc3449b64a","tid":647783,"uid":1121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T06:42:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3256/d3256851.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3256%2Fd3256851.jpg&h=39523f26&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲戴雅娜經常在IG分享性感照片。（圖／翻攝自Deyana Mounira IG）<br />\n<br />\n東尼表示戴雅娜抵達他的豪宅後，看見了他養的黑俄羅斯梗，竟然就開始逗弄狗狗的生殖器官，因此進而發生了人獸交情形。對此，戴雅娜則表示東尼根本一派胡言，還反擊說是東尼一直要狗狗來碰觸她的身體，表示自己才是被性騷擾的受害者。<br />\n<br />\n戴雅娜指稱拍攝當天，東尼不但對她說「移動妳的屁股讓牠聞聞」，還對狗狗煽動說「X她、上她」等語，隨後又把她帶進房間裡亂摸性騷擾。只是東尼的律師反駁，表示如果當天有發生任何的強迫行為，為何戴雅娜不停止數小時的拍攝行程，而且還在鏡頭面前露出笑容"},{"pid":"7296fe4d2665f083c2b00bc4d095011914a8b806","tid":647783,"uid":11962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T06:46:17.000Z","msg":"個屎忽隆到呢"},{"pid":"830033537cc17e1c1acf0e12278bcfcbcb6c260e","tid":647783,"uid":10511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T06:50:04.000Z","msg":"奶油犬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7fdd38d4e615fe3f33dda9b6753e68bc4f53b24a","tid":647783,"uid":117477,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T06:53:59.000Z","msg":"4千萬新台幣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n台灣新聞作多過真"},{"pid":"0c025f04e205a68c298c4629c2fe559c139e2d73","tid":647783,"uid":154538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T07:00:06.000Z","msg":"名副其實比狗屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d03ba34a3a97781df7530d944c02ed8f7730d35","tid":647783,"uid":12021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T07:02:17.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"213afdec3ecd8df04532da249c6be54f36e0cd5c","tid":647783,"uid":1121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T07:54:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e8bdbbbd85f0b56cc3ed639e48f6683450c835a","tid":647783,"uid":156363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T08:05:25.000Z","msg":"早幾年丹麥仲合法可以玩"}]}